    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/e62ac0f8ec2de865c0632a02085c5f1d.poster.avif?t=1764265098\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/e62ac0f8ec2de865c0632a02085c5f1d.webm?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/e62ac0f8ec2de865c0632a02085c5f1d.mp4?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐怖元素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《致命喘息》整部游戏的开发全部围绕着一个怪物的诞生，它是有史以来由人工智能所创造的最强大的怪物之一。这个怪物被设计出来，不光是为了猎杀玩家，也是为了折磨和玩弄他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/dc9cb0725639f7aff77d8795c937343f.poster.avif?t=1764265098\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/dc9cb0725639f7aff77d8795c937343f.webm?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/dc9cb0725639f7aff77d8795c937343f.mp4?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为素材而生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作专为up主的实况视频和主播的直播效果打造。欢迎来到恐怖游戏界的新纪元。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/8286628ce7b8396f40e83a6fd3e1941d.poster.avif?t=1764265098\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/8286628ce7b8396f40e83a6fd3e1941d.webm?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/8286628ce7b8396f40e83a6fd3e1941d.mp4?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >谜题与剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作采用的环境叙事会让玩家在探索中了解剧情。不会有各种笔记来拖慢游戏进度，有的只是配音演员们深厚的功底，以及横跨数千年之叙事的精华浓缩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/03bfb976be5bcfef101645025f2ad637.poster.avif?t=1764265098\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/03bfb976be5bcfef101645025f2ad637.webm?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305120/extras/03bfb976be5bcfef101645025f2ad637.mp4?t=1764265098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
